---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
const pageTitle = "privacy";
---

<BaseLayout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
    <div class="privacy-policy">
        <div class="block">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        </div>
        <p class="updated">Last updated: June 9, 2025</p>

        <p>
            Thank you for visiting our blog. We are committed to maintaining
            your privacy and protecting your personal information. This Privacy
            Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard data on this
            website, which is built with Next.js, uses Markdown for content, and
            is hosted on Vercel.
        </p>

        <h2>1. Personal Information</h2>
        <p>
            We do not require user registration or logins to access the content
            of this website. However, when you use our contact form, you may be
            asked to provide information such as your name, email address, and
            message.
        </p>
        <p>
            This contact form is powered by{" "}
            <a
                href="https://formsubmit.co/"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer">FormSubmit</a
            >, a third-party form handling service. Any data submitted via the
            form is sent directly to our email address and is not stored on our
            servers.
        </p>
        <p>
            We do not use this data for marketing or advertising purposes. It is
            solely used to respond to inquiries and is never shared or sold.
        </p>

        <h2>2. Hosting and Metadata</h2>
        <p>
            This site is hosted on <a
                href="https://vercel.com/"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer">Vercel</a
            >. Like most web hosts, Vercel may collect basic technical metadata
            for analytics and security purposes. This may include:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>IP address</li>
            <li>Browser version</li>
            <li>Device type and operating system</li>
            <li>Pages visited and time spent</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
            This data is anonymized and not associated with individual users. We
            do not access or store this information ourselves.
        </p>

        <h2>3. AI-Generated Content and Images</h2>
        <p>
            All visual content including illustrations and banners on this blog
            are created using AI tools such as DALL·E or similar. These images
            are not real photographs or depictions of actual people or events,
            and are intended solely for artistic or illustrative use.
        </p>
        <p>
            Textual content may also include AI assistance for grammar,
            structure, or drafting, but all ideas and conclusions are
            editorially reviewed.
        </p>

        <h2>4. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
        <p>
            This website does not use cookies for tracking, advertising, or
            personalization. We do not embed Google Analytics, Facebook Pixel,
            or any other third-party trackers.
        </p>

        <h2>5. External Links</h2>
        <p>
            This website may include links to other websites or platforms. We
            are not responsible for the privacy practices or content of these
            external sites.
        </p>

        <h2>6. Policy Updates</h2>
        <p>
            We may update this policy from time to time. All changes will be
            reflected on this page with the “Last updated” date clearly stated
            at the top.
        </p>

        <h2>7. Contact</h2>
        <p>
            If you have questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please
            visit our <a href="/contact">Contact</a> page to reach out.
        </p>
    </div>
</BaseLayout>
